 `types.go`\n- [ ] **2.9** Define `UpdateAgentRuntimeRequest` struct in `types.go`\n- [ ] **2.10** Define `UpdateCodeInterpreterRequest` struct in `types.go`\n- [ ] **2.11** Define `Config` struct in `server.go` - server configuration\n- [ ] **2.12** Define `Server` struct in `server.go` - HTTP server wrapper\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Service Interface Implementation\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Define `WorkloadManager` interface in `service.go`\n- [ ] **3.2** Implement `workloadManagerImpl` struct in `service.go`\n- [ ] **3.3** Implement `NewWorkloadManager` constructor function\n- [ ] **3.4** Implement `CreateAgentRuntime` method\n- [ ] **3.5** Implement `GetAgentRuntime` method\n- [ ] **3.6** Implement `ListAgentRuntimes` method\n- [ ] **3.7** Implement `UpdateAgentRuntime` method\n- [ ] **3.8** Implement `DeleteAgentRuntime` method\n- [ ] **3.9** Implement `UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus` method\n- [ ] **3.10** Implement `CreateCodeInterpreter` method\n- [ ] **3.11** Implement `GetCodeInterpreter` method\n- [ ] **3.12** Implement `ListCodeInterpreters` method\n- [ ] **3.13** Implement `UpdateCodeInterpreter` method\n- [ ] **3.14** Implement `DeleteCodeInterpreter` method\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Kubernetes Client Integration\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Implement `NewK8sClient` function in `client.go` - create Kubernetes clientset\n- [ ] **4.2** Implement `NewClientset` function in `client.go` - create typed clientset for AgentCube CRDs\n- [ ] **4.3** Implement `NewInformerFactory` function in `client.go` - create SharedInformerFactory\n- [ ] **4.4** Implement `RegisterInformers` method in `server.go` - register AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter informers\n- [ ] **4.5** Implement `StartInformers` method in `server.go` - start informers and wait for cache sync\n- [ ] **4.6** Wire up listers in `Server` struct after informer sync\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: HTTP Handlers\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/agentruntime.go`\n- [ ] **5.2** Implement `HandleCreateAgentRuntime` handler in `agentru